{"tid":661054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋最新輪候時間突破5.1年  !","createTime":"2018-05-11T08:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T15:06:53.000Z","uid":28366,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"02f53627b577b5a47d92330a2084ab448ecdbbc8","tid":661054,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/161443_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F161443_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ac112541&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公屋輪候冊公佈最新輪候宗數，一般申請者的輪候時間已突破5年，至最新的5.1年，遠超平均3年的上樓目標。根據房委會資料，截至今年3月底，公屋輪候冊上申請者達27.23萬，較上個季度下跌1.06萬。當中一般公屋申請約有15.33萬宗；配額及計分制下的非長者一人申請則有11.9萬宗。不過，一般申請者的平均輪候時間已增至5.1年，當中長者一人申請者的平均輪候時間為2.8年。<br />\n<br />\n在2017年12月底，公屋輪候冊的申請宗數達28.29萬，其中一般申請為15.51萬，配額及計分制下的非長者一人申請為12.78萬，一般申請者的平均輪候時間為4.7年，當中長者一人申請者的平均輪候時間為2.6年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180511/58179302\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180511%2F58179302&d=cvraUpSWqjSd0pn6kM4YLv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=99a59951\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180511%2F58179302&h=04836eaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180511/58179302</a>"},{"pid":"71e89c70858132d38be9e5d3e844ef86d1f1475f","tid":661054,"uid":111573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"咁多支那人，唔好話普通隊，公墓隊都排撚到仆街啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd548fdd7684f3aaa491d85e100b17c154d0cf3","tid":661054,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"